		<div id="comment_body_64498757"><p><div class="quote"><p>And I feel like we don't actually have to pay their pension anymore.</p></div><p>I'll say this again, for the millionth time: if wrongful death settlements came out of police pensions, the "Blue Knights" would quickly eliminate the "bad apples" in their ranks</p></div>
